# Drop the user's 3D model here.

Expected paths used by `lib/modelConfig.ts`:

- `/models/main-model.glb`        — primary model (the rover, astronaut, etc.)
- `/models/main-model-low.glb`    — optional lightweight version for the loading scene

Both files are optional. If neither is present, a procedural proxy
rover will render so the page is never blank.

To compress / optimise a model with `gltf-transform`:

  npx gltf-transform optimize main-model.glb main-model.optimized.glb
